People will hate you  rate you  break you  and shake you. How strong you stand is what makes you. Sometimes those who don't socialize much aren't actually anti-social  they just have no tolerance for drama and fake people. I think one of the greatest feelings in the world is when someone openly tells you how much you mean to them. stuff like that is so rare. Everyone has three lives: a public life  a private life  and a secret life Before you assume  try asking first. I admit  I really miss how things used to be. But I can also admit  that I've accepted the fact that things have changed. You were born to make mistakes  not to fake perfection. Trust someone who can see 3 things in you: the sorrow behind your smile  the love behind your anger and the reason behind your silence. An ugly personality can easily destroy a pretty face. Nothing is permanent. Especially people. Don't have your hopes high  friends become strangers  lovers become friends. And people leave. Fake friends are no different than shadows  they stick around during your brightest moments  but disappear during your darkest hours. I don‚Äôt think people understand how stressful it is to explain what‚Äôs going on in your head when you don‚Äôt even understand it yourself. Success is no accident. It is hard work  perseverance  learning  studying  sacrifice and most of all  love of what you are doing. Psychology says - no matter how angry you get  you always end up forgiving the people you love. If my daughter doesn't grow up thinking that I'm her best friend & that she can come to me for everything  then I have failed in life. Sometimes you just need to step outside  get some fresh air  clear your head  and remind yourself of who you are and where you want to be. The world is going to judge you  no matter what you do. So live your life the way you want to. It's funny how you can do nice things for people all the time  and they never notice. But once you make one mistake  it's never forgotten. Never pursue a career because others want you to. You'll be the one spending half your life at that job. Pursue your passion. Just because I tweet something doesn't mean it's relevant to my current situation. My tweets are a reflection of my thoughts  not my life

column1: H.G. Wells Success is my only option. "Arise! Awake! And stop not till the goal is reached" - "The way to develop self-confidence is to do the thing you fear and get a record of successful experiences behind you." - William Jennings "Think big  think fast  think ahead. Ideas are no one's monopoly." When deeds speak  words are nothing. Today is the only day. Yesterday is gone. You must do the things you think you cannot do. Let us remember: One book  one pen  one child  and one teacher can change the world. Change your thoughts and you change your world.
